casebody.data:
Thomas Kenneth ABRAHAM, dba Paddle Tramps Manufacturing Company, petitioner,
v.
ALPHA CHI OMEGA, et al. No. 12-1341. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 7, 2013. Case below, 708 F.3d 614 .

Motion of Law Professors for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit denied.
